{"word":"ἐπιφαίνω","slug":"ἐπιφαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπιφαίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φαίνω\">φαίνω</a></el>] ‘make an appearance’, of heavenly luminaries <b>shine, give light <a href='B:490 1:79'>Lk 1:79</a>; <a href='B:510 27:20'>Ac 27:20</a></b> (the point being that the stars could not be seen)<b>.</b> Pass. in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b>appear,</b> in imagery of divine beneficence <b><a href='B:630 2:11'>Tit 2:11</a>; <a href='B:630 3:4'>3:4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιτυχεῖν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιφᾶναι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}